Keep updated
You can update your Conan version by pip install -U conan
https://docs.conan.io/en/latest/installation.html#update
%
What is new
All releases are documented in Conan changelog
https://docs.conan.io/en/latest/changelog.html
%
Prefer Python 3
Python 2 is only fully supported until Conan 1.6
https://docs.conan.io/en/latest/installation.html#python-2-deprecation-notice
%
Use conanfile.py for consumers
You can use a conanfile.py for installing/consuming packages instead of conanfile.txt only
https://docs.conan.io/en/latest/mastering/conanfile_py.html#use-conanfile-py-for-consumers
